name: Cory M.
text: Normally I am very happy with the subs at this location but my last trip was horrible. I ordered a steak and cheese and another sub for my son. When I showed up it was close to closing and you could tell someone was in a hurry to get out of …More

name: Nathan Gold
text: The food is cheap and generally pretty good. Fair amount of seating and usually clean interior. Many but not all employees tend to be quite rude and the J1 workers often have an attitude.

name: Rob
text: Terrible even for a chain. Cold meatball subs, stale bread, rude stoner employees. Several times ordered online, got a confirmation, and showed up to see a paper sign saying they closed hours before their site or google said they did. All three strikes used up. Never again.

name: Ben Howard
text: Service was nice but the food wasn't great. Came quickly, but was underwhelming. I got the chicken number 9. Lots of bread but not a lot of substance. My wife was happy to get a cookie but disappointed by the taste. When was the last time a cookie disappointed you?

name: Patty Rodericks
text: One of the better places for a sandwich. Like this one in Chatham.
